General.Name: LAMF Global Ventures Corp. I Warrant
General.Description: LAMF Global Ventures Corp. I focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to pursue an acquisition opportunity in media, entertainment, and sports, as well as e-commerce and technology industries. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in West Hollywood, California.
